        "TileImage": "$($repository 047bef31-022a-47c6-958b-f2a20e0a3576).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47. There are only two members of Operation Skyfall left: the last lieutenant and the leader. Slight problem, however - both of their identities are encrypted. ICA hasn&apos;t been able to find them, which is where you come in. There are two hackers in Berlin, Germany who have access to the names. Eliminate them and we should be able to extract the data and track down these bastards.\r\rI will leave you to prepare.",
